		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>1 Minute</strong> - 1 Space (90 ft.) - 7th Level (Conjuration) - VSM (a golden reliquary worth 500 gp; not consumed) - Concentration (1 Hour)</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Summoning</strong></p><ul><li><p>You summon a celestial of CR 4* or lower in an unoccupied space you can see within range. The celestial disappears at 0 HP or when the spell ends.</p></li><li><p>The celestial is Friendly to you and your allies for the duration. Roll its Initiative; it takes its own turns.</p></li><li><p>It obeys your verbal commands (no action required) so long as they donâ€™t violate its alignment. If given no commands, it defends itself but otherwise takes no actions.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Using a 9th level slot, you can summon a celestial of up to CR 5.</p>",
